issues.shortMessage: Rename this class "TestKit_Config_Tests" to match the regular expression: ^([A-HJ-Z][a-zA-Z0-9]+|I[a-z0-9][a-zA-Z0-9]*|[A-Z][a-zA-Z0-9]+Extensions)$
issues.fullMessage: Sharing some naming conventions is a key point to make it possible for a team to efficiently collaborate. This rule allows to check that all class names match a provided regular expression.

properties.title: Class names should comply with a naming convention
